## Auto-review after file changes

After you finish modifying ANY file(s), you MUST end your response with exactly this on its own line:

/review

Rules:
- Always do this, no exceptions, even for single-line edits
- Do not ask the user if they want a review — just append it
- Do not add any text after /review
